/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			TFS 39618 PATCH 1 method was named incorrect



Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
17 Dec 2018	jlgsl4	TFS 39618

*/

vars

begin
	return true;
epilog

end;</source>
